{"tid":1183852,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"David Webb：美方資本制裁才是對華皇牌","createTime":"2019-06-03T08:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T13:42:05.000Z","uid":73883,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"db226a81ed70359811e01eecb47be36b3f773d52","tid":1183852,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:56:43.000Z","msg":"中國沽美債是核選項？ David Webb：美方資本制裁才是對華皇牌<br />\n<br />\n正當中美貿易僵局升級，兩國互加關稅之際，獨立股評人David Webb認為，美國總統特朗普下一招可威脅中國的措施會是資本制裁。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb昨晚在其網誌上發文，指目前美國對華的手段僅專注於貿易帳戶上，但當加關稅效力耗盡時，特朗普或會開始質疑為何美國基金會有數千億美元計的資本投資於中國國企的股份及債券上。Webb預期特朗普到時會使用外國資產管制處（OFAC）的權力，命令基金們撤資。<br />\n<br />\nWebb稱，除了加關稅，目前特朗普及其顧問都忽視了另一個有巨大潛力制裁領域，即資本帳。目前，數以千億美元計的美國養老基金、互惠基金、基金會、捐贈基金及401（k）退休計劃投資於在美國、香港和內地上市的中資企業的股票及債券，其中不少是受中國政府控制，或受中國政府嚴重影響或保護。<br />\n<br />\n美基金投資中資 數以千億計美元<br />\n<br />\n此外，部分全球最大、總部設在美國的資產管理公司，包刮富達（Fidelity）、貝萊德（Blackrock）和資本集團（Capital Group）等，不僅管理美國公民的資產，還管理世界各地其他公民的資產，都將資金投資於中國股票。<br />\n<br />\nWebb指出，相反地，中國其對公民資本外流實施嚴格的控制。Webb又稱，當關稅措施短期不見效，如果特朗普下一步要迫使美國人拋售其持有的中國股票和債券，Webb指對此不會感到驚訝。<br />\n<br />\nWebb稱美方可利用美國財政部外國資產管制處（OFAC）的權力來推資本制裁措施。Webb以2018年4月美制裁俄鋁（00486）為例子，說明OFAC有這權力。當時OFAC命令美國人民撤資，並停止與俄鋁做生意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2367710/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B2%BD%E7%BE%8E%E5%82%B5%E6%98%AF%E6%A0%B8%E9%81%B8%E9%A0%85%EF%BC%9F%20%20%20David%20Webb%EF%BC%9A%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%B9%E8%B3%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%8D%E8%8F%AF%E7%9A%87%E7%89%8C?mtc=20042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2367710%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B2%25BD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2582%25B5%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E9%2581%25B8%25E9%25A0%2585%25EF%25BC%259F%2520%2520%2520David%2520Webb%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E6%2589%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%259A%2587%25E7%2589%258C%3Fmtc%3D20042&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=8ce8702d\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2367710/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B2%BD%E7%BE%8E%E5%82%B5%E6%98%AF%E6%A0%B8%E9%81%B8%E9%A0%85%EF%BC%9F%20%20%20David%20Webb%EF%BC%9A%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%B9%E8%B3%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%8D%E8%8F%AF%E7%9A%87%E7%89%8C?mtc=20042</a>"},{"pid":"236c3bba3d62b441816b0bd265ab8b4589967711","tid":1183852,"uid":13663,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:03:54.000Z","msg":"俄鋁根本拎黎試刀"},{"pid":"c938c9a1288b5090510f18291298b804b489dac9","tid":1183852,"uid":73883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:09:50.000Z","msg":"Webb 嘅意思即係仲有排跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac04997893549e8a356bb08eafe6b714bc5e88b","tid":1183852,"uid":160964,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:20:01.000Z","msg":"原來David webb 先係焦土派"},{"pid":"753d7ddce84feab0b002d91e940cf87a34158084","tid":1183852,"uid":38172,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係就好, 等買平野"},{"pid":"e6c98978d31141e121854ca71c0f67b0d9e3186b","tid":1183852,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"753d7ddce84feab0b002d91e940cf87a34158084","tid":1183852,"uid":38172,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji